@SmitGardhariya After reading the comments on your questions, it seems to me, that you want to use websockets because another client needs to connect to mosquitto using websockets. What i found out, was that mosquitto can listen to websockets AND the normal mqtt connections. You can add an extra listener in the config file:

`listener 9001
protocol websockets`

